  • Property Details

    • canvasListener

      @NotNull public final @NotNull javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyObjectProperty<BoundCanvas.CanvasListener> canvasListenerProperty

      Returns the ReadOnlyObjectProperty containing the BoundCanvas.CanvasListener instance that is called to redraw whenever this BoundCanvas is repainted.

      Details

      1. If the BoundCanvas.CanvasListener is set to null, no additional redrawing operations will be executed.
      2. Default repaint operations are still performed.
      See Also:
      getCanvasListener(), setCanvasListener(BoundCanvas.CanvasListener)
